sourcesContent: export const isObject=e=>e&&"object"==typeof e;export const renameProp=(e,t,{[e]:r,...c})=>({[t]:r,...c});export const copyObject=e=>isObject(e)?e instanceof Array?[...e]:{...e}:e;export const omitObject=(e,t)=>{if(!isObject(e))return e;if(e instanceof Array)return[...e];const r={...e};return t.forEach((e=>r[e]&&delete r[e])),r};export const cleanObject=e=>{if(!isObject(e))return e;if(e instanceof Array)return[...e];const t={...e};return Object.keys(t).forEach((e=>{void 0!==t[e]&&null!==t[e]||delete t[e]})),t};export const cleanObjectKeys=(e,t=[])=>{if(!isObject(e))return e;if(e instanceof Array)return[...e];const r={...e};return t.forEach((e=>{r[e]&&delete r[e]})),r};export const getKeyValue=(e,t)=>isObject(e)?e instanceof Array?[...e]:e[t]:e;
